<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Forgot Password - OTP Code</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">
        <h2>Forgot Password - OTP Code</h2>
        <p>Dear Member,</p>
        <p>You are receiving this email because a request has been made to reset the password for your account.</p>
        <p>Your OTP code is: <strong>{{optCode}}</strong></p>
        <p>This OTP code is valid for a single use and will expire in {{expireTime}} minutes.</p>
        <p>If you did not make this request, please ignore this email.</p>
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p>Our Support Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
